lead_paragraph: Dawn Staley wasn't disappointed or angry that No. 6 South Carolina was tied with ninth-ranked UCLA at half. She believed she had the Bruins right where her team wanted.

headline.print_headline: Coates Leads No. 6 South Carolina Women Over UCLA 66-57
